This is the README file for Lingua::ZH::Wrap, a simple Chinese text
wrapper.

Please type "perldoc Lingua::ZH::Wrap" after installation to see
the module usage information.

* Installation

Lingua::ZH::Wrap uses the standard perl module install process:

cpansign -v		# optional; see SIGNATURE for details
perl Makefile.PL
make			# or 'nmake' on Win32
make test
make install

